description: ICICI Prudential Mutual Fund - ICICI Prudential Nifty 100 ETF is an exchange traded fund co-launched by ICICI Bank Ltd. and Prudential plc. The fund is managed by ICICI Prudential Asset Management Company Limited. It invests in the public equity markets of India. The fund seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It invests in the stocks of companies across all market capitalizations. The fund seeks to replicate the performance of the CNX 100 Index, by investing in the stocks of companies as per their weightings in the Index. It was formerly known as ICICI Prudential Mutual Fund - ICICI Prudential Nifty 100 iWIN ETF. ICICI Prudential Mutual Fund - ICICI Prudential Nifty 100 ETF was formed on August 20, 2013 and is domiciled in India.
name: ICICI Prudential Nifty 100 ETF
